WEBVTT

00:00:25.993 --> 00:00:30.083
inatuambia kwamba ulimwengu
unapanuka kwa kasi sana.

00:00:30.085 --> 00:00:31.695
Je vipi kuhusu mbeleni?

00:00:31.695 --> 00:00:35.095
Tunajua namna gani ulimwengu wetu
utafikia kikomo?

00:00:35.095 --> 00:00:38.685
Wanakosmolojia wana nadharia tatu
za swali hili,

00:00:38.685 --> 00:00:40.415
zinazoitwa Mgando Mkubwa,

00:00:40.415 --> 00:00:43.855
Mraruo Mkubwa na Uchakacho Mkubwa.

00:00:43.855 --> 00:00:46.215
Kuzielewa hizi nadharia tatu,

00:00:46.215 --> 00:00:49.885
waza vitu viwili vya kuwakilisha galaksi.

00:00:49.885 --> 00:00:53.425
Kamba ya mpira fupi, iliyokaza
inazishikilia pamoja---

00:00:53.425 --> 00:00:56.235
hiyo ni mvuto wa nguvu ya uvutano.

00:00:56.235 --> 00:00:59.725
Wakati huo huo, koleo mbili
zinaziachanisha---

00:00:59.725 --> 00:01:03.495
hiyo ni nguvu ya muasi inayofanya
ulimwengu usambae.